s=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/architect\">架构师路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">RAG 知识库</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-emerald-500 to-teal-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">RAG 知识库</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">企业级 RAG 架构设计</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->90分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>架构师路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/rag/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/rag/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/rag/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>知识架构设计</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">知识分类体系</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">建立多层次分类结构，支持按部门、主题、敏感等级分类：</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1\"><li>• 一级：公司制度 | 产品文档 | 技术规范</li><li>• 二级：HR制度 | 财务制度 | IT制度...</li><li>• 标签：公开 | 内部 | 机密</li></ul></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">元数据与过滤</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">为每个文档添加丰富元数据，检索时进行过滤：</p><div class=\"bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs mt-2\"><span class=\"text-purple-600\">查询：</span> &quot;差旅费报销流程&quot;<span class=\"text-blue-600 ml-2\">过滤条件：</span>部门=销售 | 有效期=2024年及以后</div></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">权限控制</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">基于用户角色和部门限制知识访问范围（检索前过滤）：</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1\"><li>• HR 只能访问 HR 相关文档</li><li>• 机密文档仅授权用户可见</li><li>• 跨部门协作需申请权限</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>大规模部署</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-orange-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">分布式向量数据库</h5><ul class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 space-y-2\"><li>• <strong>Pinecone</strong>：托管服务，自动扩缩容</li><li>• <strong>Milvus</strong>：开源，支持分布式部署</li><li>• <strong>Qdrant</strong>：轻量级，高性能</li><li>• <strong>Weaviate</strong>：自带向量化</li></ul></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">多租户架构</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">多个客户/部门共享基础设施但数据隔离：</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1\"><li>• 每个租户独立的 Collection</li><li>• 查询时按 tenant_id 过滤</li><li>• 独立的配额和监控</li></ul></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">增量更新机制</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600\">只更新变化的部分，而非全量重建：</p><ul class=\"text-xs text-gray-600 mt-2 space-y-1\"><li>• 监控文档变更（文件监控、数据库 CDC）</li><li>• 增量向量化和索引</li><li>• 文档删除和软删除机制</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/architect\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->架构师路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[87161,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[40715,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[78691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[30470,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n9:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\nc:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\ne:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\n10:I[92691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.6dsdn7g3rv..css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0.q-h669a_dqa.wo